snippet.title: Dodonpachi Resurrection Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/464450

The legendary bullet-hell shoot-’em-up series has come to Steam! The past is being altered. An android, known as Next EXY, has traveled one thousand years back in time. Can she really stop the war? Your task is to stop NEXY and the other Elemental Dolls who once protected humanity.

http://www.degicagames.com/
https://twitter.com/DegiGames
https://www.facebook.com/DegicaGames/
